Description: Windows-style clipboard manager for Ubuntu
 ClipVault brings the Windows Win+V clipboard history experience to Ubuntu.
 Press Super+V to toggle your clipboard history panel.
 .
 Features include clipboard history for text and images, pinning important
 items, searching through history, one-click paste, and a system tray icon.
